node.text:
The renown Patek Philippe Aquanaut but from Tiffany & Co. The stunning 40mm timepiece is crafted in 18k rose gold and attached on a brown rubber strap. This edition features the "Tiffany & Co." stamp at 6 o'clock to stand apart from the rest. What are your thoughts on this timepiece? 

Would you wear it? Leave your comments below!

node.title: Unboxing: Patek Philippe Aquanaut Tiffany & Co. Edition

node.text: The Rolex Pearlmaster 39 is Rolex's crowning jewelry watch. Featuring the softly curved lines of the Pearlmaster design, it is characterized by uniquely rich dials and exquisite gem settings. Dressed in an 18kt Everrose gold and diamond set lugs, the Pearlmaster features a diamond set bezel and a roman dial that houses an impressive 713 diamonds. The Pearlmaster holds a special place in the Oyster collection, it represents the height of exquisiteness with precious metals and gemstones. Powered by the 3235 caliber, the Pearlmaster 86405RBR features a power reserve of 70 hours, and is waterproof up to 100 meters or 330 feet.

node.title: Unboxing: Rolex Pearlmaster 39 Factory Diamond Set

node.text:
CEO, @avi_hiaeve / Avi Hiaeve and the Avi & Co. team fly down to California to personally meet Nile Niami and Producer Michael at the world's largest house, "The One" in Bel Air. Join us as we take a tour of this magnificent home and view some of the worlds most luxurious timepieces.

What was your favorite scene of this trip? Leave your comments below! 🤩

node.title: Vlog: Avi & Co. fly down to “The One” in Bel Air

What are your thoughts on this timepiece? Comment Below!

The renown Patek Philippe Aquanaut but from Tiffany & Co. The stunning 40mm timepiece is crafted in 18k rose gold and attached on a brown rubber strap. This edition features the "Tiffany & Co." stamp at 6 o'clock to stand apart from the rest. What are your thoughts on this timepiece? 

Would you wear it? Leave your comments below!
